#: .uk.EQUIPMENT_PASSIVEHEALING_UNCOMMON_PICKUP
msgctxt ".uk.EQUIPMENT_PASSIVEHEALING_UNCOMMON_PICKUP"
msgid ""
"{0}\n"
"<sprite name=\"Quality\"> Activate on an ally to teleport it to you and "
"create a ghost in its place."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.EQUIPMENT_PASSIVEHEALING_UNCOMMON_DESC
msgid ""
"Gain a Woodsprite follower that heals a friendly target for "
"<style=cIsHealing>10% of their maximum health</style> instantly, then "
"<style=cIsHealing>1.5% of your maximum health</style> every second. "
"Activating the equipment assigns a new target, or yourself if there are no "
"targets available.\n"
"Activating the equipment on an ally <style=cIsUtility>teleports</style> it "
"to you, and creates a <style=cIsDamage>ghost</style> in its original place "
"with <style=cIsDamage>200% damage</style> and lasts for <sprite "
"name=\"Quality\"> <style=cIsUtility>15 seconds</style>. Can have a maximum "
"of <sprite name=\"Quality\"> <style=cIsUtility>1</style> ghost at a time."
msgstr ""

