#: .uk.ITEM_TOOTH_UNCOMMON_PICKUP
msgctxt ".uk.ITEM_TOOTH_UNCOMMON_PICKUP"
msgid ""
"{0}\n"
"<sprite name=\"Quality\"> Healing orbs gain an additional buff depending on "
"the skill used."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.ITEM_TOOTH_UNCOMMON_DESC
msgid ""
"{0}\n"
"Healing orbs gain an additional buff depending on the skill used to kill the "
"enemy. Killing with your <style=cIsUtility>primary skill</style> grants "
"<sprite name=\"Quality\"> <style=cIsDamage>20%</style> attack speed for "
"<sprite name=\"Quality\"> <style=cIsUtility>1</style> <style=cStack>(+1 per "
"stack)</style> second(s). Killing with your <style=cIsUtility>secondary "
"skill</style> grants <sprite name=\"Quality\"> <style=cIsDamage>5%</style> "
"secondary skill damage for <sprite name=\"Quality\"> <style=cIsUtility>2</"
"style> <style=cStack>(+2 per stack)</style> seconds. Killing with your "
"<style=cIsUtility>utility skill</style> grants <style=cIsHealing>barrier</"
"style> for <sprite name=\"Quality\"> <style=cIsHealing>15 health</style> "
"<style=cStack>(+15 per stack)</style>. Killing with your <style=cIsUtility>"
"special skill</style> reduces all non-special skill cooldowns by <sprite "
"name=\"Quality\"> <style=cIsUtility>1</style> <style=cStack>(+1 per stack)</"
"style> second(s)."
msgstr ""

